LivehelpGenie,allows,users,to,chat,with,their,site,visitors,in,real,time,and,track,visitors,movements,across,the,website,Users,can,also,create,and,manage,canned,responses,block,unwanted,IP,addresses,and,attach,persistent,notes,to,visitors,in,case,they,return,later,or,need,to,be,transferred,to,another,operator,The,live,chat,feature,is,fully,customizable,and,brandable,All,chats,are,SSL,encrypted,LivehelpGenie,provides,a,SOAP,API,for,managing,users,and,resellers